N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 318.12 - Audit

State Regulations

The Chair may conduct periodic audits on employers, self-insurers, carriers and the State Insurance Fund concerning any information
or payment related to assessments. Notes
